<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Tools for running shows.">
    <title>ShowMaker</title>
    <%= javascript_tag :homepage, async: false %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="splash-container">
        <div class="panel splash">
          <h1 class="splash-head">ShowMaker</h1>
          <p class="splash-subhead">
            Successfull events made easy
          </p>
          <a href="#signup" class="signup-link">Sign up</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="content">

          <div class="panel info">
            <p>
              With ShowMaker you can embed show listings, information and ticket sales into your website.
            </p>
            <p>
              Once tickets are purchased, use our easy box-office interface to check guests into the show and/or make sales at the door.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h2 class="content-head is-center">ShowMaker can help you:</h2>

          <h3 class="content-subhead">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            Take your events to the next level
          </h3>
          <p>
            We're creating a platform for clubs and promoters to use to drive interest in their shows and to conduct ticket sales online and at the door.
          </p>

          <h3 class="content-subhead">
            <i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i>
            Engage your audience.
          </h3>
          <p>
            Booking the best acts in the world won't help you if no-one knows they're coming to your venue.  Use our tools to run a cross-media campaign with integrated mailing lists, FB, Twitter & Instagram postings.
          </p>

          <h3 class="content-subhead">
            <i class="fas fa-ticket-alt" data-fa-transform="rotate-330"></i>
            Sell tickets online and at the door
          </h3>
          <p>
            Embed an upcoming show listing into your existing website and sell tickets right from the listings.
          </p>
          <p>
            Use our app to scan the tickets at the door, or take door sales using credit cards.
          </p>

          <h3 class="content-subhead">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            No show too large or small.
          </h3>
          <p>
            ShowMaker was born out of the frustration we felt as event center owners who
            book and promote acts.  It's a lot of work to put together a successful event,
            but our software can make it easier.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <header>
            <h2 class="signup">
              Signup for Showmaker
              <span class="start-at">
                Plans start at just $20 per month!
              </span>
            </h2>
          </header>
          <div class="flex planslist">
            <div class="plan">
              <ul>
                <li>120 tickets per show</li>
                <li>5 shows per month</li>
                <li>Maximum 1000 mailing list subscribers</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="price"><sup>$</sup>20/month</p>
            </div>
            <div class="plan">
              <ul>
                <li>500 tickets per show</li>
                <li>12 shows per month</li>
                <li>Unlimited mailing list subscribers</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="price"><sup>$</sup>50/month</p>
            </div>
            <div class="plan">
              <ul>
                <li>2,000 tickets per show</li>
                <li>Unlimited shows</li>
                <li>Unlimited mailing list subscribers</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="price"><sup>$</sup>100/month</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h4>
            You will be prompted to choose between one of the above
            plans after you login for the first time
          </h4>
          <%= erb :signup, locals: { hide_title: true, params: {}, tenant: false } %>
        </div>
        <%= erb :footer %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
